<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idee08e5b1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idee08e5b2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For effective date of section, see <ref href="/us/pl/92/516/s4">section 4 of Pub. L. 92–516</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s136">section 136 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
